<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-green);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">MEPH</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Mechanical &amp; HVAC</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Heating, cooling and ventilation are the heart of any building's services — and the package most likely to derail a programme if it's handled badly. We self-deliver the full mechanical scope, from plant rooms and pipework to AHUs and BMS controls, so it sits with one accountable team from survey through to witnessed commissioning.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Mechanical &amp; HVAC →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Mechanical &amp; HVAC,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Heating &amp; cooling systems</li><li>Ventilation &amp; air handling units</li><li>Heat pumps &amp; low-carbon plant</li><li>Plant rooms &amp; pipework</li><li>Pumps, valves &amp; distribution</li><li>BMS &amp; controls integration</li><li>Witnessed commissioning &amp; handover</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>CIBSE &amp; BSRIA commissioning codes</li><li>Building Regs Part L &amp; F</li><li>F-Gas Regulations compliance</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you design as well as install?</summary><p>Both. We can develop a consultant's mechanical design through to installation, or design-and-build from the brief — including load modelling, plant selection and coordination.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover heat pumps and low-carbon plant?</summary><p>Yes. Air-source heat-pump retrofits and low-carbon plant are a growing part of our work, alongside the electrical-distribution upgrades they typically need.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How is the mechanical work commissioned?</summary><p>Systems are commissioned to CIBSE and BSRIA codes with witnessed performance testing, and we hand over a full set of O&amp;M and as-built records.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/meph/">MEPH overview</a><a class="sector" href="/meph/electrical/">Electrical</a><a class="sector" href="/meph/public-health/">Public Health</a><a class="sector" href="/meph/data-infrastructure/">Data &amp; IT infrastructure</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top xlinks" data-xlink><div clas